{"title":"到站了","date":"2018-04-29T17:22:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年4月30日","L":"2018/04/30","MM-DD":"04-30"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/30/7DZhql4OtLKVPy9.jpg","link":"2018/04/30/到站了","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-01-09T17:48:33.093Z","content":"<p>我靠在你的肩膀上\n感受着你的鼻息\n温暖\n呼吸的起伏</p>\n<p>一起都静了下来\n我捕捉着你的心跳\n感受着自己的\n他们彼此交错</p>\n<p>前一下是你的过去\n下一次是你的未来\n我徘徊着踟蹰着</p>\n<p>不甘心留在你的过去\n更无法陪你到未来\n到站了......</p>\n","prev":{"title":"照亮","link":"2018/07/08/照亮"},"next":{"title":"我望着你","link":"2018/04/18/我望着你"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/30/到站了/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/30/到站了/\" title=\"到站了\">http://wardzhou.art/2018/04/30/到站了/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}